{"id":232674606,"title":"《夜裏無星》","content":"http://i.imgur.com/bYUX9PY.jpg\n\n深夜兩點，夜裏的空氣是如此凜冽，嗅進肺部的冰涼中帶著濕氣，氣溫好似又降了幾度，灰黑色的大衣幾乎沒能好好幫我抵禦寒氣。意識因為烈酒而顯得迷濛，體溫隨之上升，腦袋暈地厲害，腳卻騰空升起。\n\n那一片原是酒瓶的碎玻璃隨著越離開地面而模糊不清，碎片邊緣融成一塊，漸漸揉進在月光下發出淡淡光芒的銀灰色柏油路中。\n再往上一些，僅有的幾支路燈輕微閃爍了起來，只要再遠些，看著便像恆星了。\n只差一點，就能摘下月了，我的指尖幾乎觸碰到了，我幾乎就要觸碰到了那縷凝寂。\n\n最後我仍跌落在超商外的階梯上，沒能抓住月亮，手上的酒瓶內只剩下一口的餘量，而月光被散落在腳邊的玻璃碎片撕得碎碎的。\n街上無人，夜裏無星。\n\n\n\n＿馬村雀雀醬／希小姐\nhttps://www.instagram.com/chuchu_write/?igshid=1b1bdktg1l6ec","excerpt":"深夜兩點，夜裏的空氣是如此凜冽，嗅進肺部的冰涼中帶著濕氣，氣溫好似又降了幾度，灰黑色的大衣幾乎沒能好好幫我抵禦寒氣。意識因為烈酒而顯得迷濛，體溫隨之上升，腦袋暈地厲害，腳卻騰空升起。那一片原是酒瓶的碎","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-12T14:25:47.534Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-12T14:25:47.534Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":5,"tags":[],"topics":["馬村雀雀醬","希小姐"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"大仁科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":5}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/bYUX9PY.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"535ddbcf-ae80-4eea-9811-1439ce15b50f","url":"https://i.imgur.com/bYUX9PYl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/bYUX9PYl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/bYUX9PYl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-12T14:25:47.534Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-12T14:25:47.534Z"},{"id":"535ddbcf-ae80-4eea-9811-1439ce15b50f","url":"http://i.imgur.com/bYUX9PY.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/bYUX9PY","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/bYUX9PYl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-12T14:25:47.534Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-12T14:25:47.534Z"}],"postAvatar":""}